    <p>The Three Horizons progression ensures systematic capability building: start with personal AI mastery, develop team-AI collaboration, then scale to organizational AI intelligence. Each horizon builds on the previous one, creating compound advantages that become sustainable competitive advantages.</p>

    <hr />

    <p><em>Teams that master collaborative intelligence will define the future of work. The question isn't whether AI will transform team dynamics—it's whether your team will lead this transformation or react to it.</em></p>
